headline: Zillow (Z) Q2 Earnings Lag Estimates
summary: Zillow (Z) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -9.09% and +1.31%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
